KYOGRE has the power to create massive
rain clouds that cover the entire sky
and bring about torrential downpours. This POKMON saved people who were
suffering from droughts.

KYOGRE is named in mythology as the
POKMON that expanded the sea by
covering the land with torrential rains and towering tidal waves.
It took to sleep after a cataclysmic
battle with GROUDON.

KYOGRE has appeared in mythology as the
creator of the sea. After long years of
feuding with GROUDON, it took to sleep at
the bottom of the sea.

This POKMON is said to have
expanded the sea by bringing heavy rains.
It has the power to control water.

Grce  lnergie de la nature, il peut accomplir

Ce pouvoir lui permet dappeler de terribles dluges
pour tendre les mers.

Mithilfe von Naturenergie kann es eine Protomorphose
durchfhren und so seine ursprngliche Form zurckerlangen.
Dadurch kann es Strme erzeugen und das Meer vergrern.

Kyogre se sirve de la energa de la naturaleza para realizar su
Regresin Primigenia y recobrar su apariencia primitiva. Con tal
poder, puede desencadenar tempestades para expandir los
ocanos.

Lenergia della natura pu causare larcheorisveglio
di questo Pokmon, facendolo tornare al suo aspetto
originario.
Pu provocare diluvi torrenziali in grado di espandere
la superficie dei mari.

Through Primal Reversion and with natures
full power, it will take back its true form. It can
summon storms that cause the sea levels to rise.

Un Pokmon considr comme lavatar des ocans.
Selon les lgendes, il a disput de nombreux combats
avec Groudon pour contrler lnergie de la nature.

Es heit, Kyogre sei die Personifizierung des Meeres.
Legenden zufolge hat es in seinem Bestreben, sich die
Naturenergie anzueignen, viele Male gegen Groudon gekmpft.

A Kyogre siempre se le ha descrito como el Pokmon que
expandi los ocanos. Varias leyendas cuentan que libr
combates contra Groudon en repetidas ocasiones para tener
el control de la energa de la naturaleza.

Si dice che questo Pokmon abbia un profondo
legame con le distese dei mari.
Le leggende narrano dei suoi continui scontri con
Groudon per ottenere lenergia della natura.

Kyogre is said to be the personification of the sea itself.
Legends tell of its many clashes against Groudon,
as each sought to gain the power of nature.
